notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Here that, Boys?  This boy has a problem with our righteous crusade.  Let's see if we can persuade him otherwise."
 NPCFemaleText "Here that, Boys?  This little lady has a problem with our righteous crusade.  Let's see if we can persuade her otherwise."
      options {
              }
}
Node "Good"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
/* Skill checks for node Good. */

      define_skill_check Skill_Check_005_Speech {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = -20;
      onsuccess => Test;
      onfailure => Doubt_It;
      }

{
NPCText "Good.  Now, are you going to join or not?"
 NPCFemaleText "Good.  Now, are you going to join or not?"
      options {
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yes...sir." linkto "Skill_Check_005_Speech"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No, I think I'll just kick your ass and walk away.  How's that sound?\n" linkto "combat"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Not right now, thanks.  Bye!" linkto "Death"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Shades_Of_Gray"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
/* Skill checks for node Shades_Of_Gray */

      define_skill_check Skill_Check_006_Speech {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = -15;
      onsuccess => Great_Purge;
      onfailure => Spy;
      }

{
NPCText "What the Thieves do is plunder and kill for no reason.  They are lawless, bloodthristy, and cruel.  We only take what we need from local settlements for our noble cause.  If people get in our way, then we have no choice but to put them down.  Chances are, they were working with the Villians of the wastes anyway.  That is the point of the Great Purge."
      options {
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Great Purge?" linkto "Skill_Check_006_Speech"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How are you better than the \"viallins of the wastes\" then?  What seperates the \"Good\" form the \"Evil\" here?" linkto "Purging"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So you'll kill millions just to \"spread righteousness\"?  You're crazy if you think that you can get anywhere near your goal.  You don't have the manpower." linkto "Numbers"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Exactly"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
/* Skill checks for node Exactly */

      define_skill_check Skill_Check_007_Speech {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = -15;
      onsuccess => Great_Purge;
      onfailure => Spy;
      }

{
NPCText "I'm glad to find another person so supportive of out cause.  Would you like to know more of the Great Purge?"
      options {
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Oh, yes, please tell me, oh holy one." linkto "Skill_Check_007_Speech"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No, but I would like to ask you something." linkto "Yes"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I really should be leaving...." linkto "Death"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Kiddies"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
/* Skill checks for node Kiddies */

      define_skill_check Skill_Check_008_Speech {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = -15;
      onsuccess => Numbers_CLONE;
      onfailure => Doubt_It;
      }

{
NPCText "Even children are corrupted by the seeds of evil sown in the Wastes.  They too must be eliminated to prevent the spreading of evil."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I thought that you guys were only fighting the \"villains of the wastes\"?  How does this make you any better than them?" linkto "Purging"  notes ""
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see clearly now, Colonel!  But how will we purge the wastes?  We are so few..." linkto "Skill_Check_008_Speech"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Damn your sick. Nothing a good blast to the face won't cure.  Time for your medicine, old man!" linkto "Crazy"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "McArthur"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Some evil seems good, just as some good seems evil.  You must not be deceived, <PC>.  The McArthurs must be killed."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What crime have they comitted?" linkto "Crime2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So killing children justifies the causes of righteousness?  If that's the way you think, then you're no better than any of the \"villians of the wastes\"." linkto "Purging"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see now!  Yes, they must die!  But before I go, can I ask you something?" linkto "Yes"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Excellent"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Great!  Go, and shed the evil blood in the name of righteousness!"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Just one last question." linkto "Yes"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Oh, I'll shed blood allright. I hope you lived a good life, old man, because it's about to end." linkto "combat"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You are one sick puppy.  Time to put you down." linkto "Crazy"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Purging"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
/* Skill checks for node Purging */

      define_skill_check Skill_Check_009_Speech {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = -5;
      onsuccess => Numbers_CLONE;
      onfailure => Spy;
      }

{
NPCText "But you don't see!  All of the Wasteland is corrupted!  All that are not fighting for the cause of the KFC must be purged, incuding the children!  The seed must not be corrupted by the wickedness of their parents!  Only in death is their purity.  Once the wasteland is cleansed, there will be peace for the righteous!"
      options {
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yes, I see now!  ...So, how will we bring about this Purge?" linkto "Skill_Check_009_Speech"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Right...has anyone told you that you are completely insane?" linkto "Crazy"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hmm.  I have a better idea.  I kick your ass and walk away.  How's that \"Purge\" sound?" linkto "combat"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Crime2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
/* Skill checks for node Crime2 */

      define_skill_check Skill_Check_010_Speech {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = -10;
      onsuccess => Numbers_CLONE;
      onfailure => Spy;
      }

{
NPCText "It's not about comitting crime, it's about preventing it.  Wickedness is in all the hearts of people.  Only those who fight for our cause are truly pure and righteous. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Uh-Huh.  Well, I think I've heard enough. Time for you to meet your maker." linkto "combat"  notes ""
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Oh yes, how could I not have seen before!  Tell me, though, how will we stop this evil from spreading?  Show me, oh holy one." linkto "Skill_Check_010_Speech"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I..uh..I think I had better be...uh..leaving." linkto "Death"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Numbers"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "That's where you're wrong, Son.  You see, my Great-Grandfather started the KFC's true crusade against evil.  He and the rest of the majority of the members of his Vault staged a revolt agaisnt the Vault overseer.  Using the wepaons and technology salvaged from the Vault, he established a stronghold of righteousness in the Wasteland.  We have been slowly growing ever since.  Our biggest set of luck came when the Powers of Righteousness themselves showed us an old military base, all but decimated in the Great War.  Or so it looked.  My Grandfather lead an expedition into the ruins of the base to discover a tresure trove of wepons, ammunition, more powerful than anything he had ever seen.  He also found several robots, which were non-functioning at the time.  After looking at some Vault-manuals on Programming and Repair, a team of our Scientists re-activated the robots and began constructing more at the Vault.  Our numbers are bolstered every day in Humans and in Machines. soon, the Great Purge will be ready to begin.  We have hundreds of troops, all armed and trained with the best equipment and most deadly weapons.  Our name, the \"Kentucky\" fighting chickens is only used to throw the wicked into thinking that we are based in the north, and to honor my Great-Great-Great-Grandfather, who came up with the idea of our crusade.  I can't tell you where our base is exactly until I trust you more, but i can tell you that it is close, like a sheperd watching it's wayward flock. "
 NPCFemaleText "That's where you're wrong, little lady.  You see, my Great-Grandfather started the KFC's true crusade against evil.  He and the rest of the majority of the members of his Vault staged a revolt agaisnt the Vault overseer.  Using the wepaons and technology salvaged from the Vault, he established a stronghold of righteousness in the Wasteland.  We have been slowly growing ever since.  Our biggest set of luck came when the Powers of Righteousness themselves showed us an old military base, all but decimated in the Great War.  Or so it looked.  My Grandfather lead an expedition into the ruins of the base to discover a tresure trove of wepons, ammunition, more powerful than anything he had ever seen.  He also found several robots, which were non-functioning at the time.  After looking at some Vault-manuals on Programming and Repair, a team of our Scientists re-activated the robots and began constructing more at the Vault.  Our numbers are bolstered every day in Humans and in Machines. soon, the Great Purge will be ready to begin.  We have hundreds of troops, all armed and trained with the best equipment and most deadly weapons.  Our name, the \"Kentucky\" fighting chickens is only used to throw the wicked into thinking that we are based in the north, and to honor my Great-Great-Great-Grandfather, who came up with the idea of our crusade.  I can't tell you where our base is exactly until I trust you more, but i can tell you that it is close, like a sheperd watching it's wayward flock. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wow.  I need to kill you, you sick bastard." linkto "Crazy"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Damn.  You're nuts.  Thanks for telling me about your secret base, now I can end your sick crusade.  Time to put you down, old man." linkto "Crazy"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I heard all I needed to hear.  Now die." linkto "combat"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You forgot one thing, oh holy one." linkto "What"  notes ""
              }
}
