Node "Numbers_CLONE"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Well, most of our plan is already completed.  You see,  my Great-Grandfather started the KFC's true crusade against evil.  He and the majority of the members of his Vault staged a revolt against the Vault overseer.  Using the weapons and technology salvaged from the Vault, he established a stronghold of righteousness in the Wasteland.  We have been slowly growing ever since.  Our biggest set of luck came when the Powers of Righteousness themselves showed us an old military base, all but decimated in the Great War.  Or so it looked.  My Grandfather lead an expedition into the ruins of the base to discover a stockpile, ammunition, weapons, and armor deep within the irradiated base.  More powerful than anything he had ever seen.  He also found several robots, which were non-functioning at the time.  After looking at some Vault-manuals on Programming and Repair, a team of our Scientists brought the robots back to the Vault for study and eventaul replication.  Our numbers are bolstered every day in Human Newborns, Comers-of-age, and in Machines.  Soon, the Great Purge will be ready to begin.  We have hundreds of troops, all armed and trained with the best equipment and most deadly weapons.  Our name, the \"Kentucky\" fighting chickens is only used to throw the wicked into thinking that we are based in the north, and to honor my Great-Great-Great-Grandfather, who came up with the idea of our crusade.  I can't tell you where our base is exactly until I trust you more, but I can tell you that it is close, like a sheperd watching it's wayward flock. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wow.  I need to kill you, you sick bastard." linkto "Crazy"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Damn.  You're nuts.  Thanks for telling me about your secret base, now I can end your sick crusade.  Time to put you down, old man." linkto "Crazy"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I heard all I needed to hear.  Now die." linkto "combat"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You forgot one thing, oh holy one." linkto "What"  notes ""
              }
}
